tool_description: Generate/Check if a username is available on various platforms like Facebook, instagram, tiktok, snapchat and other social media platforms! You can also check if  a domain is registered or not.
name: Check Username
title: Check Username

api_list.name: Dribbble
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://check-username.p.rapidapi.com/check/dribbble/username"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "check-username.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
